I'm a 34 DD and I LOVE, LOVE, LOVE these sports bras!
I wear one to work each day because they provide support, yet are SUPER comfortable!
When I workout, I usually run and I have to put on 2 of these bras, but, I guess that's the plague of having huge boobs.
I have yet to find a sports bra that gives me the hold and support that I need when running with just one bra.
But, at least with these bras, like I said before, they're so comfortable, EVEN with 2 of them on!
I love the zipper because I hate having to pull a bra over my head, and it makes it easier to take them on and off when I'm wet or sweaty, which is a plus.
